{"word":"Women","slug":"women","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Women</b> Creation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=27'>Gen 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=22'>Gen 2:22</a><br/> Named<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=23'>Gen 2:23</a><br/> Fall of, and curse upon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=16'>Gen 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=3'>2Co 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=14'>1Ti 2:14</a><br/> Promise to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=15'>Gen 3:15</a><br/> Had separate apartments in dwellings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=67'>Gen 24:67</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=33'>Gen 31:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=9'>Est 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=11'>Est 2:11</a><br/> Veiled the face<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=65'>Gen 24:65</a><br/><a href='S:Veil'>Veil</a> <br/> Vows of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=30&verse=16'>Num 30:16</a><br/> When jealously charged with infidelity, guilt or innocence to be determined by trial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=31'>Num 5:31</a><br/> Took part in ancient worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=21'>Exo 15:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=8'>Exo 38:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=22'>1Sa 2:22</a><br/> Took part in choir<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=6'>1Ch 25:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=65'>Ezr 2:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=67'>Neh 7:67</a><br/> Worshiped in separate compartments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=8'>Exo 38:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=22'>1Sa 2:22</a><br/> Consecrated jewels to tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=22'>Exo 35:22</a><br/> Consecrated mirrors to tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=8'>Exo 38:8</a><br/> Required to attend reading of the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=12'>Deu 31:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=35'>Jos 8:35</a><br/> Purifications of:<br/> - After menstruation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=33'>Lev 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=4'>2Sa 11:4</a> <br/> - After childbirth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=22'>Luk 2:22</a> <br/> Difference in ceremonies made between male and female children<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a><br/> Religious privileges of, among early Christians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=14'>Act 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=13'>Act 12:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=11&verse=5'>1Co 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=34'>1Co 14:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Ti 2:11</a><br/> Domestic duties of women:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=6'>Gen 18:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=19'>Pro 31:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=41'>Mat 24:41</a> <br/> - Cooked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=6'>Gen 18:6</a> <br/> - Spun<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=26'>Exo 35:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=19'>1Sa 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=24'>Pro 31:24</a> <br/> - Embroidered<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=22'>Pro 31:22</a> <br/> - Made garments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=39'>Act 9:39</a> <br/> - Gleaned<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=8'>Rth 2:8</a> <br/> - Kept vineyards<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=1&verse=6'>Son 1:6</a> <br/> - Tended flocks and herds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=11'>Gen 24:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=14'>Gen 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=20'>Gen 24:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=9'>Gen 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=16'>Exo 2:16</a> <br/> - Worked in fields<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=27&verse=11'>Isa 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=6'>Eze 26:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=8'>Eze 26:8</a> <br/> - Was doorkeeper<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=69'>Mat 26:69</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=17'>Joh 18:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=14'>Act 12:14</a> <br/> Forbidden to wear men's costume<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=5'>Deu 22:5</a><br/> Wore hair long<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=11&verse=15'>1Co 11:15</a><br/> Rules for dress of Christian<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=10'>1Ti 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=4'>1Pe 3:4</a><br/> Ornaments of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=23'>Isa 3:23</a><br/> Weaker than men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=7'>1Pe 3:7</a><br/> Are timid<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=19&verse=16'>Isa 19:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=37'>Jer 50:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=30'>Jer 51:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=3&verse=13'>Nah 3:13</a><br/> Are affectionate<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=26'>2Sa 1:26</a><br/> Are tender to her off-spring<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=49&verse=15'>Isa 49:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=10'>Lam 4:10</a><br/> Are mirthsome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=34'>Jdg 11:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=21'>Jdg 21:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=13'>Jer 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=17'>Zec 9:17</a><br/> Are courteous to strangers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=17'>Gen 24:17</a><br/> Could not marry without consent of parents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=4'>Gen 24:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=6'>Gen 34:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=17'>Exo 22:17</a><br/> Not to be given in marriage considered a calamity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=37'>Jdg 11:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=63'>Psa 78:63</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=4&verse=1'>Isa 4:1</a><br/> Taken captive<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=9'>Num 31:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=15'>Num 31:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=18'>Num 31:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=35'>Num 31:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=1&verse=18'>Lam 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=30&verse=18'>Eze 30:18</a><br/> Punishment to be inflicted on men for seducing:<br/> - When betrothed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=27'>Deu 22:27</a> <br/> - When not betrothed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=17'>Exo 22:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=29'>Deu 22:29</a> <br/> Treated with cruelty in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=25'>Deu 32:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=21'>Lam 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=5&verse=11'>Lam 5:11</a><br/> Virtuous, held in high estimation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=3&verse=11'>Rth 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=30'>Pro 31:30</a><br/> Fond of self-indulgence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=32&verse=11'>Isa 32:11</a><br/> Fond of ornaments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=32'>Jer 2:32</a><br/> Subtle and deceitful<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=29'>Pro 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=35'>Pro 6:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=27'>Pro 7:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=26'>Ecc 7:26</a><br/> Silly, and easily led into error<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=3&verse=6'>2Ti 3:6</a><br/> Zealous in promoting superstition and idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jer 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=17'>Eze 13:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=23'>Eze 13:23</a><br/> Active in instigating to iniquity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=16'>Num 31:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=25'>1Ki 21:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=26'>Neh 13:26</a><br/> Guilty of sodomy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=7'>2Ki 23:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=26'>Rom 1:26</a><br/> As rulers:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=12'>Isa 3:12</a> <br/> - Deborah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=4'>Jdg 4:4</a> <br/> - Athaliah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=16'>2Ki 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=3'>2Ch 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=12'>2Ch 22:12</a> <br/> - Queen of Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=13'>1Ki 10:13</a> <br/> - Candace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=27'>Act 8:27</a> <br/> - Persian queen sat on throne with the king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=6'>Neh 2:6</a> <br/> Patriotic:<br/> - Patriotic:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=20'>Exo 15:20</a> <br/> - Deborah<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - Women of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=6'>1Sa 18:6</a> <br/> - Women of the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=20'>2Sa 1:20</a> <br/> Aid in defensive operations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=53'>Jdg 9:53</a><br/> As poets:<br/> - Miriam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=21'>Exo 15:21</a> <br/> - Deborah<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - Hannah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=10'>1Sa 2:10</a> <br/> - Elizabeth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=45'>Luk 1:45</a> <br/> - Mary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=55'>Luk 1:55</a> <br/> As Prophets:<br/> - Miriam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=21'>Exo 15:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=4'>Mic 6:4</a> <br/> - Deborah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=5'>Jdg 4:5</a> <br/> - Huldah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=20'>2Ki 22:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=28'>2Ch 34:28</a> <br/> - Noadiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=14'>Neh 6:14</a> <br/> - Anna<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=38'>Luk 2:38</a> <br/> - Philip's daughters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=9'>Act 21:9</a> <br/> False prophets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=13&verse=23'>Eze 13:23</a><br/> In business<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=18'>Pro 31:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=24'>Pro 31:24</a><br/> Property rights of:<br/> - In inheritance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=11'>Num 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=36&verse=13'>Num 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=6'>Jos 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=42&verse=15'>Job 42:15</a> <br/> - To sell real estate<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=9'>Rth 4:9</a> <br/> Sold for husband's debts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=25'>Mat 18:25</a><br/> First to sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=6'>Gen 3:6</a><br/> Last at the cross<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=56'>Mat 27:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=41'>Mar 15:41</a><br/> First at the sepulcher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=47'>Mar 15:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=6'>Mar 16:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=28'>Luk 23:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=49'>Luk 23:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=56'>Luk 23:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=10'>Luk 24:10</a><br/> First to whom the risen Lord appeared<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=9'>Mar 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=18'>Joh 20:18</a><br/> Converted by preaching of Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=15'>Act 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=4'>Act 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=12'>Act 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=34'>Act 17:34</a><br/> Social status of women:<br/> - In Persia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=22'>Est 1:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=12'>Dan 5:12</a> <br/> - In Roman customs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=24'>Act 24:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=25&verse=13'>Act 25:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=25&verse=23'>Act 25:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=30'>Act 26:30</a> <br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=18'>Gen 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=24'>Gen 2:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=16'>Gen 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=22'>Est 1:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=16'>Pro 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=11&verse=22'>Pro 11:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=12&verse=4'>Pro 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=14&verse=1'>Pro 14:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=18&verse=22'>Pro 18:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=19&verse=14'>Pro 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=9'>Pro 21:9</a>;