/a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=14'>Eze 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=26'>Rom 1:26</a> <br/> - Zeal of, in licentious practices of idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=7'>2Ki 23:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=14'>Hos 4:14</a> <br/> - Guileful and licentious<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=2&verse=19'>Pro 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=5&verse=20'>Pro 5:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=29'>Pro 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=35'>Pro 6:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=27'>Pro 7:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=26'>Ecc 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=32'>Eze 16:32</a> <br/> - Commits forgery<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=8'>1Ki 21:8</a> <br/> - Silly and wayward<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=3&verse=6'>2Ti 3:6</a> <br/> - Instances of:<br/> b Eve, in yielding to temptation and seducing her husband<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=6'>Gen 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=14'>1Ti 2:14</a><br/> b Sarah, in her jealousy and malice toward Hagar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=11'>Gen 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=21'>Gen 21:21</a><br/> b Lot's wife, in her rebellion against her situation, and against the destruction of Sodom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=26'>Gen 19:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=32'>Luk 17:32</a><