ood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=10'>Act 5:10</a><br/> b the woman taken in adultery and brought to Jesus in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=8&verse=11'>Joh 8:11</a><br/> b Figurative:<br/> b of backsliding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=2'>Jer 6:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=17&verse=4'>Rev 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=17&verse=18'>Rev 17:18</a><br/> b of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=32&verse=9'>Isa 32:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=32&verse=11'>Isa 32:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=13'>Mat 25:13</a><br/> b Symbolic of wickedness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=5&verse=8'>Zec 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=17'>Rev 17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=2'>Rev 19:2</a><br/><a href='S:Wife'>Wife</a>"}]}